<D>__{you're doing very nicely, puff. i'm pleased.}
<A>__{the slide changes to another picture of the same woman, this time she is naked, has her back to the camera, is sticking her butt out, and looking over her shoulder at the viewer with shiny, heavily lipsticked, pursed lips. puff is shaking.}
