<D>__{great...}
<A>__{puff leaps out of his chair screaming and lunges for the screen. nathan grabs the black box and jolts him. puff goes flying in the air and lands with a crack. he heaves for a while, then leaps up and runs for the screen again. again nathan shocks him. again he lands on the floor. he heaves, stands, lunges for the screen again. nathan shocks him. this happens seven more times. smoke is pouring out from the collar. puff struggles to his feet. looks at the screen. he shrugs.}
